                    while n < 16
                      - n = n+1
                      a.col-sm-4(href='../../img/videos/36/'+n+'.jpg' data-toggle='lightbox' data-gallery='example-gallery')
                        img.img-fluid(src='../../img/videos/36/'+n+'.jpg')
            p.
              The third fight was the most intense and exciting of all three, with <b>Christina Shvets</b> struggling hard against big and strong <b>Victoria Vardugina</b>. The winner was declared only after the end of the 3rd round. Christina won the first round with a choke, but in the next two rounds, to her disappointment, she was defeated (choked) by Victoria, though she struggled desperately up to the very last second.
