                        img.img-fluid(src='../../img/videos/37/2/'+n+'.jpg')
            p.
              <b>Victoria Vardugina</b>,  <b>Daria Uvarova</b>  and  <b>Christina Shvets</b>  eventually won the 1st, 2nd and 3rd places respectively.
